title: Create wireframes for homepage
notes: Include mobile and desktop versions. Focus on user flow and accessibility.

title: Design new color palette
notes: Consider brand guidelines and accessibility contrast ratios.

title: Implement responsive navigation
notes: Ensure mobile-first approach with hamburger menu for small screens.

title: Optimize images for web
notes: Use WebP format where possible. Target 80% quality for balance of size and quality.

title: Set up development environment
notes: Include Docker configuration and development database setup.

title: Create user authentication flow
notes: Implement OAuth integration with Google and GitHub. Include password recovery flow.

title: Design app icon and splash screen
notes: Create versions for iOS and Android. Follow platform-specific guidelines.

title: Research target audience
notes: Survey 200+ potential users. Focus on demographics and usage patterns.

title: Create social media content calendar
notes: Plan content for Q2 across Instagram, Twitter, and LinkedIn. Include key campaign dates.

title: Document API endpoints
notes: Use OpenAPI specification. Include authentication requirements and example requests.
